2014年6月4日，三名[[蒙克顿|蒙克顿]]市[[皇家加拿大骑警|皇家加拿大骑警]]警察枪击遇害，两名警察负伤<ref name="CBC RCMP">{{cite news|title=3 RCMP officers dead, 2 wounded in Moncton shooting|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/3-rcmp-officers-dead-2-wounded-in-moncton-shooting-1.2665359|accessdate=5 June 2014|agency=CBC|date=4 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140605032321/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/3-rcmp-officers-dead-2-wounded-in-moncton-shooting-1.2665359|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月5日，警方开始连夜追捕24岁的枪手贾斯丁·布尔科，6月6日将其抓获，至此长达28小时的搜捕行动告终<ref name="NatPost" /><ref name="twitter1">{{cite web |url=https://twitter.com/GRCNB/status/474770369870446595 |title=GRCNB: Justin Bourque arrêté par GRCNB à 00 h 10 à Moncton. Il est détenu par la police. 1/2 |language=fr |publisher=Twitter.com |date=2014-06-05 |accessdate=2014-06-06 |archive-date=2014-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607011748/https://twitter.com/GRCNB/status/474770369870446595 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2005年时，曾发生过导致四名皇家骑警遇害的{{link-en|美亚霍普悲剧|Mayerthorpe tragedy}}。这起枪击案也是2010年来蒙克顿市的第一宗凶杀案<ref name=bbc>[http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-27721569 "Moncton shooting: City on lockdown during manhunt"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-27721569 |date=20140607011310 }}, BBC</ref><ref name="Canadian police charge suspect over shooting deaths of three Mounties">{{cite news |author=Associated Press in Moncton |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/06/canadian-mountie-shooting-suspect-arrested-say-moncton-police |title=Canadian police charge suspect over shooting deaths of three Mounties |publisher=The Guardian |date=2014-06-06 |accessdate=2014-06-07 |archive-date=2014-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606215049/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/06/canadian-mountie-shooting-suspect-arrested-say-moncton-police |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Moncton shooting manhunt has quickly become one of Canada's largest police operations"/>。

== 过程 ==
=== 枪击 ===
这起事件于当地时间2014年6月4日下午7点20分发生。警察接报称有一名身穿迷彩服的男子，携带两把长枪和一支弩<ref name="NatPost" />。只要在运输过程中枪内没有子弹，公开携带非限制枪支在加拿大是合法的<ref>{{cite web|last1=Royal Canadian Mounted Police|title=Storing, Transporting and Displaying Firearms|url=http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/cfp-pcaf/fs-fd/storage-entreposage-eng.htm|accessdate=5 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606211557/http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/cfp-pcaf/fs-fd/storage-entreposage-eng.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。枪手伏击与警方爆发枪战，三名警察在枪战中遇害，两名警察中弹住院，未有生命危险<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite news|work=CBC News|title=Moncton shooting: Finding, arresting suspect 'top priority'|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-finding-arresting-suspect-top-priority-1.2665707|accessdate=5 June 2014|archive-date=2019-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213055147/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-finding-arresting-suspect-top-priority-1.2665707|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NY Daily"/><ref name="m919">[http://www.news919.com/2014/06/04/three-rcmp-officers-shot-dead-in-moncton/ "Three RMCP officers shot dead in Moncton"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.news919.com/2014/06/04/three-rcmp-officers-shot-dead-in-moncton/ |date=20140606234853 }}, [[News919|News919]], June 4, 2014.</ref>。据目击者表示，枪手设下埋伏时，与几名平民搭讪，事后没有向平民开枪。其他目击者报告称，枪手居然对企图帮助警察的人员挥手示意离开<ref name="autogenerated1"/><ref name="Moncton shooter waved away civilian who tried to help fallen officer, witness says">{{cite news|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/06/05/moncton-shooting-how-it-happened/ |title=Moncton shooter waved away civilian who tried to help fallen officer, witness says |publisher=National Post |date=2014-06-05 |accessdate=2014-06-07}}</ref>。[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]报道称电视画面显示，“几辆车的窗户被打破或是留有弹孔”<ref name=nyt>{{cite news|last1=Austen|first1=Ian|title=Police Hunt Killer of Canadian Officers|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/06/world/americas/police-hunt-killer-of-canadian-officers.html|work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|date=5 June 2014|accessdate=2014-06-07|archive-date=2014-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606234119/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/06/06/world/americas/police-hunt-killer-of-canadian-officers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。枪手随后逃离现场。蒙克顿西北区被封锁以寻找枪手，公交车从街上驶离，通往被封锁区域的入口被封锁<ref name="CNN">{{cite news|title=Shooter on the loose after killing 3 officers in New Brunswick, Canada|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/06/04/world/americas/canada-shooting/|accessdate=June 4, 2014|agency=CNN|date=June 4, 2014|author=Dana Ford|author2=Greg Botelho|archive-date=2014-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140608002525/http://www.cnn.com/2014/06/04/world/americas/canada-shooting|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 追捕 ===
当局将24岁贾斯汀·布尔科锁定为犯罪嫌疑人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/27709330|title=Canada shooting: Manhunt as police officers killed in Moncton|date=5 June 2014|accessdate=5 June 2014|publisher=BBC News|quote=Police said they were searching for Justin Bourque, 24, who was "armed and dangerous", and tweeted a picture of a suspect with weapons|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607232916/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/27709330|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在进行搜捕的第二天，警方和市民发现多处疑犯踪迹。超过300名警务人员参与搜捕<ref>{{cite news|title=Moncton shooting: RCMP brief media on manhunt|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-rcmp-brief-media-on-manhunt-1.2665707|publisher=CBC|date=5 June 2014|accessdate=5 June 2014|archive-date=2019-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190213055147/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-rcmp-brief-media-on-manhunt-1.2665707|dead-url=no}}</ref>，行人和驾驶员被要求远离搜索区域，公共交通暂停服务，学校、政府部门、商店和企业临时关闭<ref name=bbc/><ref name=toppriority>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-finding-arresting-suspect-top-priority-1.2665707 "Moncton shooting: Finding, arresting suspect 'top priority'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-finding-arresting-suspect-top-priority-1.2665707 |date=20190213055147 }}, [[加拿大广播公司|加拿大广播公司]]</ref>。居民奉命紧锁于家中并打开室外照明，尽量不在社交媒体发布警方行为<ref name="Moncton shooting manhunt has quickly become one of Canada's largest police operations">{{cite news|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/06/05/moncton-shooting-manhunt-has-quickly-become-one-of-canadas-largest-police-operations/ |title="Moncton shooting manhunt has quickly become one of Canada's largest police operations" |publisher=National Post |date=2014-06-05 |author=Tristin Hopper |accessdate=2014-06-06}}</ref>。

翌日，警察包围一幢公寓楼，把该楼的[[公共广播系统|公共广播系统]]切断<ref name="global news building">{{cite news|title=Manhunt in Moncton continues: Police surround apartment complex|url=http://globalnews.ca/news/1374998/rcmp-officers-shot-in-moncton-reports/|accessdate=5 June 2014|publisher=Global News|date=5 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607044744/http://globalnews.ca/news/1374998/rcmp-officers-shot-in-moncton-reports/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。下午3点，十几名全副武装的警察包围该建筑，并向楼内部署一个带摄像头的机器人。几分钟后，由于没有发现枪手踪迹，警方从公寓楼撤走，<ref name=toppriority/><ref name="global news building">{{cite news|title=Manhunt in Moncton continues: Police surround apartment complex|url=http://globalnews.ca/news/1374998/rcmp-officers-shot-in-moncton-reports/|accessdate=5 June 2014|publisher=Global News|date=5 June 2014}}</ref>后来从公寓楼打来的报警电话被证明是一场虚惊<ref name="UPDATED: Search Continues For Moncton Shooting Suspect">{{Cite web |url=http://www.cjob.com/2014/06/05/37846/ |title="UPDATED: Search Continues For Moncton Shooting Suspect" |accessdate=2014-06-07 |archive-date=2014-06-06 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140606002550/http://www.cjob.com/2014/06/05/37846/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一辆载有[[热成像仪|热成像仪]]摄影机的[[警用直升机|警用直升机]]在蒙克顿市内搜索枪手，两辆[[装甲车|装甲车]]用以运送全副武装的作战部队成员<ref name=nyt/>。

当地时间6月6日上午12点10分，枪手被警方拘捕。一名市民在麦加大道的一处院落内发现了嫌疑人后打电话报警<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/moncton-shooting-witness-michelle-thibodeau-describes-suspect-s-arrest-1.2666937 Moncton shooting: Witness Michelle Thibodeau describes suspect's arrest] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/moncton-shooting-witness-michelle-thibodeau-describes-suspect-s-arrest-1.2666937 |date=20140607053552 }} CBC News</ref><ref name="Justin Bourque faces murder, attempted murder charges in Moncton shootings">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/justin-bourque-faces-murder-attempted-murder-charges-in-moncton-shootings-1.2666996 |title=Justin Bourque faces murder, attempted murder charges in Moncton shootings |publisher=Cbc.ca |date=2014-06-06 |accessdate=2014-06-07 |archive-date=2014-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607032714/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/justin-bourque-faces-murder-attempted-murder-charges-in-moncton-shootings-1.2666996 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。蒙克顿北部长达28小时的封锁不久后被解除。据称枪手被捕时向警方疾呼：“我完事了。”<ref name="twitter1"/><ref name="Moncton shooting suspect Justin Bourque arrested">{{cite news |url=http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2014/06/06/moncton_shooting_suspect_justin_bourque_arrested.html |title=Moncton shooting suspect Justin Bourque arrested |publisher=The Star |date=2014-06-06 |accessdate=2014-06-06 |archive-date=2014-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606200532/http://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2014/06/06/moncton_shooting_suspect_justin_bourque_arrested.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 被捕时枪手赤手空拳，他的武器在现场被发现<ref name="Canadian police charge suspect over shooting deaths of three Mounties"/>。

=== 受害者 ===
三名警察在枪战中遇害，另有两人负伤。枪击案发生后两天，五名受害者的身份被公开，三名遇难者分别为：大卫·罗素，32岁，[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]{{link-en|维多利亚维尔|Victoriaville}}人；法布里斯·乔治·热沃当，[[法国|法国]][[布洛涅-比扬古|布洛涅-比扬古]]人，45岁；道格拉斯·詹姆斯·拉里彻，[[新不伦瑞克省|新不伦瑞克省]][[圣约翰_(新不伦瑞克)|圣约翰]]。两名受害者分别为埃里克·斯特凡·J.杜博思和马里·达琳·高根<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-rcmp-release-names-of-3-slain-officers-1.2666995 |title=Moncton shooting: RCMP release names of 3 slain officers |publisher=CBC.ca |date=2014-06-05 |accessdate=2014-06-06 |archive-date=2019-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105034032/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/moncton-shooting-rcmp-release-names-of-3-slain-officers-1.2666995 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 疑犯详情 ==
24岁的枪手贾斯汀·布尔科是蒙克顿居民，在枪击发生时，疑犯穿着军用[[迷彩服|迷彩服]]，头上戴着一个棕色的发带<ref name="NY Daily">{{cite news|title=Three police officers shot dead|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/cops-shot-moncton-new-brunswick-manhunt-underway-report-article-1.1817494|accessdate=June 4, 2014|work=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|NY Daily News]]|date=June 4, 2014|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607000619/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/cops-shot-moncton-new-brunswick-manhunt-underway-report-article-1.1817494|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CTV">{{cite news|title=Moncton manhunt after shooter kills three, wounds two RCMP officers|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/moncton-manhunt-after-shooter-kills-three-wounds-two-rcmp-officers-1.1853749|accessdate=June 4, 2014|agency=CTV News|date=June 4, 2014|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607095446/http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/moncton-manhunt-after-shooter-kills-three-wounds-two-rcmp-officers-1.1853749|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其犯案动机尚未明确。据称，因着迷于[[阴谋论|阴谋论]]，他最近辞去了在当地一间[[杂货店|杂货店]]的工作。平时他本人随口就谈杀人和自杀<ref name="BI"/><ref name=bang/>。

一名同事表示，布尔科在信教家庭中长大，没受过学校教育<ref name=bang/> 。另一名同事则表示，“他似乎总跟上司过不去，对父母、老板、警察也是……<ref name="BI">[http://www.businessinsider.com/justin-bourque-cop-killer-shooter-2014-6#ixzz33mc8bH2v "Exclusive: Ex-Coworker Says Suspected Cop-Killer 'Wanted To Go Out With A Bang'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/justin-bourque-cop-killer-shooter-2014-6#ixzz33mc8bH2v |date=20140608000452 }}, ''Business Insider''</ref> ”有媒体报道称他在社交媒体中发布反警方言论<ref name=nyt/>。枪击案当天，他在[[Facebook|Facebook]]发布了一张带大卫·查普尔语录说明的照片：“你熄灯时条子就过来了，可你的车子抛锚时，他们就装作没事从你身边开走。<ref name="bang">{{cite news|author=Tu Thanh Ha|script-title=en:Suspect in Moncton shooting talked about going out ‘with a bang’|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/suspect-in-moncton-shooting-talked-about-going-out-with-a-bang/article18999247/|accessdate=7 June 2014|work=The Globe and Mail|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607234253/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/suspect-in-moncton-shooting-talked-about-going-out-with-a-bang/article18999247/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="globalnews.ca">{{cite news|work=Global News|title=Who is Justin Bourque, suspect in Moncton shooting?|url=http://globalnews.ca/news/1375802/who-is-justin-bourque-suspect-in-moncton-shooting/|accessdate=5 June 2014|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607194418/http://globalnews.ca/news/1375802/who-is-justin-bourque-suspect-in-moncton-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>”

有媒体报道，布尔科的Facebook充满了图片及“偶尔关于携带武器权利的玩笑贴<ref name="BI"/>”。枪击案第二天，当地一间贩卖枪支和户外用品的商店，世界尽头仓库在其Facebook页面上发表声明，确实布尔科自称为商店雇员，但他“没有从他们那里买过枪支或弹药<ref name="globalnews.ca"/>”。布尔科的一位朋友描述，布尔科一次跟几位同事去露营时，带了一把没子弹的枪前去，那晚喝的烂醉如泥的他需要人搀扶。“那种情形把我们给吓坏了，所以下次我们没敢邀请他。”目前尚不清楚此前是否有人就布尔科持枪向警方报案<ref name="NatPost" />。在加拿大，若要申请持枪，要提交关于个人心理状态或意向的材料，以便警方调查<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Royal Canadian Mounted Police|title=Contact the Canadian Firearms Program|url=http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/cfp-pcaf/cont/index-eng.htm|accessdate=5 June 2014|archive-date=2014-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705123630/http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/cfp-pcaf/cont/index-eng.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在他的Facebook页面上，他还表示他认为加拿大“太柔软”而不能在即将到来的袭击中幸存。一次他这样回复[[第86届奥斯卡金像奖|第86届奥斯卡金像奖]]：“[[第三次世界大战|第三次世界大战]]就在我们身边，一厢情愿的想法不能够阻止其发生。这不像[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]，[[北约|北约]]和[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]及其盟友比起来极为寡不敌众<ref name="bang"/>。”三月份，他发帖警告称：“加拿大是世界上最有可能被俄罗斯侵入的目标，从而推动战争的开始。”

枪击案数小时前，布尔科发布了美国[[敲击金属|敲击金属]]乐队[[麦加帝斯|麦加帝斯]]歌曲《口中陷阱》的歌词<ref name="bang"/>。

=== 审判 ===
被捕后不久，布尔科在警方陪同下首次在蒙克顿法院出庭。他被指控三项一级谋杀罪名及两项谋杀未遂罪名。他将在7月3日回到法庭受审。在受审之前，他的辩护律师将会为审判作准备。<ref name="Canadian police charge suspect over shooting deaths of three Mounties"/><ref name="First-degree murder charges laid in deaths of 3 Moncton RCMP officers">{{cite news |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/first-degree-murder-charges-laid-in-deaths-of-3-moncton-rcmp-officers-1.1856072 |title=First-degree murder charges laid in deaths of 3 Moncton RCMP officers |publisher=Ctvnews.ca |date=2013-06-06 |accessdate=2014-06-07 |archive-date=2014-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606231833/http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/first-degree-murder-charges-laid-in-deaths-of-3-moncton-rcmp-officers-1.1856072 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据布尔科的父亲对他近期状态的描述，法官批准了辩方做精神鉴定的请求。经过精神鉴定，布尔科被宣布可以正常受审。他选择了陪审团审判并豁免了预审权。然而，在正式审判开始前，他承认了三项一级谋杀罪和两项二级谋杀罪。认罪后，检察官表示会请求在加拿大废除了[[死刑|死刑]]并在2011年通过允许对谋杀罪连判不得假释期的新刑法之后的最高刑期，即三个连续的终身监禁，并且75年不得假释（每项一级谋杀罪25年不得假释）。他的量刑听证在2014年10月17日开始。<ref name="plead">{{cite news |language = en |url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/justin-bourque-pleads-guilty-to-murdering-3-moncton-mounties-1.2730536 |title = Justin Bourque pleads guilty to murdering 3 Moncton Mounties |publisher = CBC News |date = 2014-08-08 |accessdate = 2014-08-11 |archive-date = 2014-08-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140810195325/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/new-brunswick/justin-bourque-pleads-guilty-to-murdering-3-moncton-mounties-1.2730536 |dead-url = no }}</ref>量刑听证上，检方请求了终身监禁并且75年不得假释，辩方也求判终身监禁但是不得假释期降为50年。10月31日，法官大卫·史密斯判处布尔科三个连续的终身监禁并75年不得假释。<ref name="sentence">{{cite news |language = en |url = 
http://news.nationalpost.com/2014/10/31/justin-bourque-gets-unprecedented-five-life-sentences-for-moncton-shootings/ |title =Justin Bourque handed harshest sentence since Canada’s last execution more than 50 years ago |publisher = National Post |date = 2014-10-31 |accessdate = 2014-11-05}}</ref>

== 后续 ==
枪击过后，新不伦瑞克省主席大卫·埃瓦德发表声明，称自己对杀戮感到“难以置信的悲伤”，并向遇害者家属表示慰问<ref name=bbc/><ref name=harp>{{cite web|last1=Harper|first1=Stephen|title=Statement by the Prime Minister of Canada on the death of three RCMP officers|url=http://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2014/06/05/statement-prime-minister-canada-death-three-rcmp-officers|accessdate=5 June 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607004407/http://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2014/06/05/statement-prime-minister-canada-death-three-rcmp-officers|archivedate=2014年6月7日}}</ref>。新不伦瑞克省皇家骑警指挥官兼助理处长罗杰·布朗<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/13-10-01-150623-eng.htm |title=Assistant Commissioner Roger Brown named 29th Commanding Officer of the RCMP in New Brunswick, Fredericton, N.B. |publisher=Royal Canadian Mounted Police |date=2013-10-01 |accessdate=2014-06-06 |archive-date=2014-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606232014/http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/nb/news-nouvelles/releases-communiques/13-10-01-150623-eng.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，称6月4日是“新不伦瑞克皇家骑警史上最黑暗的一天<ref name="CNN"/>”。蒙克顿市市长乔治·勒布朗在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上发表声明称，“对蒙克顿案感到极其悲伤。呆在家里让警察做他们的工作吧。为所有家庭祈祷。<ref name="UPDATED: Search Continues For Moncton Shooting Suspect"/>”[[下议院|下议院]]翌日就枪击案表质询前，向遇害者默哀片刻<ref name="autogenerated1"/>。[[加拿大总理|加拿大总理]][[史蒂芬·哈珀|史蒂芬·哈珀]]亦发表声明：“我代表所有加拿大人，劳林和我向遇害者家属、同事及受到这一惨剧影响的朋友们，致以深切的慰问，我们也祈祷受伤者能早日康复。”他还表示，这起事件提醒我们“男女执法者每天将自己的生活献给了加拿大，以保护公民和社区的安全”。<ref name="UPDATED: Search Continues For Moncton Shooting Suspect"/><ref name=harp>{{cite web|last1=Harper|first1=Stephen|title=Statement by the Prime Minister of Canada on the death of three RCMP officers|url=http://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2014/06/05/statement-prime-minister-canada-death-three-rcmp-officers|accessdate=5 June 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607004407/http://pm.gc.ca/eng/news/2014/06/05/statement-prime-minister-canada-death-three-rcmp-officers|archivedate=2014年6月7日}}</ref>皇家骑警局长鲍勃·鲍尔森发表一份关于三名遇害警察的声明：“他们的死令人费解，他们最终的牺牲将永远被铭记。<ref name="Justin Bourque faces murder, attempted murder charges in Moncton shootings"/>”在社交媒体上，#PrayforMoncton（祝福蒙克顿）话题开始走红<ref>{{cite news |url=https://ca.news.yahoo.com/photos/the-most-powerful-prayformoncton-tweets-1402004362-slideshow/ |title=The most powerful #PrayForMoncton tweets |publisher=Yahoo News Canada |date=2014-06-05 |accessdate=2014-06-07 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714143118/https://ca.news.yahoo.com/photos/the-most-powerful-prayformoncton-tweets-1402004362-slideshow/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

